reviewText: I just finished watching all the Episodes of Breaking Bad on Netflix and Amazon video then I decided to watch Weeds.  If you have seen Breaking Bad you will see the amazing similarities.  Something tells me the Writer of Breaking Bad saw Weeds. Haha
summary: Weeds is the comic drama of Breaking Bad
Title: N/A

reviewText: The acting was great.  The cast of actors played their parts as if the had lived such a life of smoke and Mary Jane.  Mary-Louise Parker and the others brought Weeds from the 1960s to the 2012s.  Weeds shows what can happen when you live a life working in the Mary Jane world.  They take you on a wild ride from a small town to Mexico, New york, etc.  It has an ending leaving a feeling that was the whole gig worth it? Lot of smoking and sex with a lot of laughs.  Art Gray
summary: Mary-Louise Park is a great actor. She is in both Red (1&2) movies. She does't do any nude takes in Red's.
